WEBVTT

00:01.058 --> 00:02.680
Hey there and welcome to Soul Church.

00:03.300 --> 00:07.104
Our prayer is that this message encourages you wherever you may be in life.

00:07.705 --> 00:12.710
We've been hearing so many stories about what God is doing in people's lives and we'd love to hear yours.

00:13.051 --> 00:17.575
So take a second and send your story to stories at soulchurch.com.

00:17.595 --> 00:21.640
Thanks again for joining us today and we hope that you enjoy the message.

00:22.060 --> 00:22.561
God bless.

00:24.363 --> 00:24.943
There we go.

00:24.963 --> 00:27.666
How good is it to see some of the one the characters?

00:27.938 --> 00:37.992
and it's even better to see so many unfamiliar faces in church today, and obviously a lot of familiar ones, and we're wishing you all a merry Christmas.

00:38.433 --> 00:40.536
Now, who loves the Christmas feeling?

00:40.556 --> 00:44.121
Give me a wave you love the Christmas feeling, getting the tree up.

00:44.943 --> 00:47.727
Where's all of our November tree people?

00:49.309 --> 00:50.871
Come on, there's nothing to be ashamed about.

00:50.891 --> 00:52.854
If your tree goes up in November, give us a wave.

00:52.894 --> 00:55.698
October.

00:56.290 --> 00:59.595
Okay, a little prayer session for you guys after the service.

01:01.518 --> 01:05.584
Any people just don't like taking the tree down, so you don't bother.

01:05.824 --> 01:06.946
