10:14.754 --> 10:17.317
The innkeeper couldn't see it in front of him, a pregnant mum.

10:17.517 --> 10:19.879
Who knows whenever there's a pregnant mum, there's a stressed out dad.

10:21.781 --> 10:25.885
Okay, so he's not just a pregnant mum, there's a stressed out dad going, come on, there must be a bed.

10:26.586 --> 10:28.888
