God bless you.

17:26.201 --> 17:26.962
God bless you.

17:27.106 --> 17:27.727
God bless you.

17:27.807 --> 17:28.408
God bless you.

17:28.528 --> 17:29.669
God bless you.

17:29.689 --> 17:30.310
God bless you.

17:30.390 --> 17:31.071
God bless you.

17:31.531 --> 17:31.952
Amazing.

17:31.972 --> 17:33.133
We're making room for Jesus.

17:33.173 --> 17:33.794
God bless you.

